                    <num>6.</num>
                    <hi rend="italic">se discoperse</hi>: ‘si mostrò’ (<hi rend="italic">TLIO</hi>, s.v. <hi rend="italic">discoprire</hi>, § 1.4).
                </note>
            </div>
